item.title: CVE-2013-0264|2024-08-06T14:18:09.556Z -- cumin -- cumin
item.description: An import error was introduced in Cumin in the code refactoring in r5310. Server certificate validation is always disabled when connecting to Aviary servers, even if the installed packages on a system support it.
